{"tid":370910,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"11月去東京近郊 住宿點安排好","createTime":"2017-08-23T10:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T14:22:05.000Z","uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88c88382420bf9761d4ddb5ccb61c5e7c5d4bb72","tid":370910,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:07:38.000Z","msg":"打算同男友去6日近郊 6日市區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近郊就想去呢啲：<br />\n輕井澤<br />\n箱根<br />\n江之島<br />\n富士山河口湖<br />\n川越<br />\n越後湯澤<br />\n<br />\n咁住宿應該點搞好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該每日轉地方？定租airbnb?定租溫泉旅館？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想方便啲又唔好咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06bc5cf99171d1366886c764cb10507fc9f390d5","tid":370910,"uid":123905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:16:06.000Z","msg":"日日搬酒店咁煩。唔住溫泉既話，即日來回啦"},{"pid":"5448f36fa2f1a10667de7cb904dcec6bd561dc0e","tid":370910,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:23:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日搬酒店咁煩。唔住溫泉既話，即日來回啦</blockquote><br />\n即日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 攰到仆街喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日來回3個鐘車程"},{"pid":"a12b1b66c98227ec27e995269f84a33ff3483ca4","tid":370910,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:43:53.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲有經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03e565e01ca3b2a8bf4a8e2da5918937469aea7","tid":370910,"uid":41562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:26:18.000Z","msg":"分幾次去<br />\n河口湖嘅airbnb都唔平"},{"pid":"c4eefdf07b20ed39716491105d3554c43c9c9fc3","tid":370910,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:34:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分幾次去<br />\n河口湖嘅airbnb都唔平</blockquote><br />\n打算6日去哂喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我岩岩睇過<br />\n呢啲地方一晚都要700<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎係係咪要辛苦啲<br />\n即日來回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1d81842e1a2fc372587e680cb224f4779fad84","tid":370910,"uid":72444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:59:41.000Z","msg":"去咁多地方 邊玩同睇得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba445766da0031a8bdffb9d74857ca0eb9d8f9f1","tid":370910,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去咁多地方 邊玩同睇得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係架 但因為budget有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n決定咗每日來回既話<br />\n咁只可以揀果日行程睇少啲野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有下次手頭鬆啲果陣再去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cef91d3099c4b92362b3fce1e0f0cd7f1caee26","tid":370910,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"江之島，川越住返東京市區就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2b2fb0fa3a22e5557369522911aeec3429c3c9","tid":370910,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>江之島，川越住返東京市區就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係wo 岩岩睇完原來好近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔算好多野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279d52838aaf10acf4f11bf682a656a7593bc737","tid":370910,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:52:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去咁多地方 邊玩同睇得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係架 但因為budget有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n決定咗每日來回既話<br />\n咁只可以揀果日行程睇少啲野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有下次手頭鬆啲果陣再去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明知自已 budget 有限就好心咪貪心學人去咁多近郊地方啦，冇錢咁樣玩搵自已笨。"},{"pid":"e8b49181cd0e6301b2a7c461e1a6881dad0c20e1","tid":370910,"uid":92462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:57:50.000Z","msg":"借個post黎搭單問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果同屋企人富士山河口湖一日遊,跟local tour呢個行程好無?<br />\n<br />\n富士山五合目(自由散步/50分鐘),河口湖(午餐/50分鐘),&lt;搭乘空中纜車/8分鐘&gt;,富士見台車站(從展望台觀賞360度美景/40分鐘*包含搭乘空中纜車的時間),御坂農園(季節水果吃到飽 / 30分),Chateau勝沼(葡萄酒試飲･購物/30分鐘)<br />\n<br />\n預定07:50-18:20<br />\n<br />\n定係有其他位更值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01bef3c57ef997cfbaea197d68300663163c5d01","tid":370910,"uid":133959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:22:04.000Z","msg":"當用東京做據點：<br />\n越後湯澤 - 有新幹線，可以即日來回<br />\n川越 - 可以即日來回<br />\n江之島 - 個人覺得半日玩唔晒，但好多人都選擇即日來回<br />\n輕井澤、箱根、河口湖都唔建議即日，尤其箱根即日不如skip<br />\n<br />\n另一方面輕井澤+越後湯澤同河口湖+箱根路程接近，可以串埋做兩個兩日一夜行程慳時間同車費<br />\n只要東京住同一間酒店，你check out可以寄行李係酒店，輕裝出發<br />\n例如東京-&gt;越後湯澤-&gt;輕井澤訓一晚-&gt;輕井澤-&gt;東京<br />\n河口湖可以安排浸一晚溫泉，當然亦可選擇箱根浸，但平均會比較貴(除左窮人恩物一の湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n如果東京要住airbnb，通常都無得寄存行李，要去車站租Locker，個人唔太prefer(除非你樓下就係主要車站)<br />\n<br />\n浸溫泉其實就豐儉由人，例如芦ノ湖一の湯我上Jalan望下而家book都係每位7000yen，不連稅但包兩餐，其實唔貴得過番東京住。其實我覺得反而住東京先貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8458aa4c910c93f355fe7847259ae31f6f85be1","tid":370910,"uid":726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去咁多地方 邊玩同睇得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係架 但因為budget有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n決定咗每日來回既話<br />\n咁只可以揀果日行程睇少啲野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有下次手頭鬆啲果陣再去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明知自已 budget 有限就好心咪貪心學人去咁多近郊地方啦，冇錢咁樣玩搵自已笨。</blockquote><br />\n河口湖點都要住返晚溫泉酒店，好正<br />\n<br />\n川越同江之島都可以即日來回<br />\n箱根加河口湖預三日左右"},{"pid":"c6b27e3942844b643805505d379f624f0186e47f","tid":370910,"uid":133959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:39:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借個post黎搭單問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果同屋企人富士山河口湖一日遊,跟local tour呢個行程好無?<br />\n<br />\n富士山五合目(自由散步/50分鐘),河口湖(午餐/50分鐘),&lt;搭乘空中纜車/8分鐘&gt;,富士見台車站(從展望台觀賞360度美景/40分鐘*包含搭乘空中纜車的時間),御坂農園(季節水果吃到飽 / 30分),Chateau勝沼(葡萄酒試飲･購物/30分鐘)<br />\n<br />\n預定07:50-18:20<br />\n<br />\n定係有其他位更值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nD點岩玩就得，個人認為河口湖唔係賞花既話無乜邊個點係一定要去，天氣好邊度都靚，天氣唔好&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139352347ca85d98616b4eb5bd7e6126ad53932d","tid":370910,"uid":92462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>借個post黎搭單問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果同屋企人富士山河口湖一日遊,跟local tour呢個行程好無?<br />\n<br />\n富士山五合目(自由散步/50分鐘),河口湖(午餐/50分鐘),&lt;搭乘空中纜車/8分鐘&gt;,富士見台車站(從展望台觀賞360度美景/40分鐘*包含搭乘空中纜車的時間),御坂農園(季節水果吃到飽 / 30分),Chateau勝沼(葡萄酒試飲･購物/30分鐘)<br />\n<br />\n預定07:50-18:20<br />\n<br />\n定係有其他位更值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nD點岩玩就得，個人認為河口湖唔係賞花既話無乜邊個點係一定要去，天氣好邊度都靚，天氣唔好&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5848b7a57493c07a20780012e0df9da0e4e0df","tid":370910,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去咁多地方 邊玩同睇得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係架 但因為budget有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n決定咗每日來回既話<br />\n咁只可以揀果日行程睇少啲野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有下次手頭鬆啲果陣再去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明知自已 budget 有限就好心咪貪心學人去咁多近郊地方啦，冇錢咁樣玩搵自已笨。</blockquote><br />\n好啦 減走兩個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3847d84e0da8ec20ae7fb81bbc89db65674104","tid":370910,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:47:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借個post黎搭單問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果同屋企人富士山河口湖一日遊,跟local tour呢個行程好無?<br />\n<br />\n富士山五合目(自由散步/50分鐘),河口湖(午餐/50分鐘),&lt;搭乘空中纜車/8分鐘&gt;,富士見台車站(從展望台觀賞360度美景/40分鐘*包含搭乘空中纜車的時間),御坂農園(季節水果吃到飽 / 30分),Chateau勝沼(葡萄酒試飲･購物/30分鐘)<br />\n<br />\n預定07:50-18:20<br />\n<br />\n定係有其他位更值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果情侶都join 係咪好odd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27c72b5c5b0370634887dd7e302763b32636912","tid":370910,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:49:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當用東京做據點：<br />\n越後湯澤 - 有新幹線，可以即日來回<br />\n川越 - 可以即日來回<br />\n江之島 - 個人覺得半日玩唔晒，但好多人都選擇即日來回<br />\n輕井澤、箱根、河口湖都唔建議即日，尤其箱根即日不如skip<br />\n<br />\n另一方面輕井澤+越後湯澤同河口湖+箱根路程接近，可以串埋做兩個兩日一夜行程慳時間同車費<br />\n只要東京住同一間酒店，你check out可以寄行李係酒店，輕裝出發<br />\n例如東京-&gt;越後湯澤-&gt;輕井澤訓一晚-&gt;輕井澤-&gt;東京<br />\n河口湖可以安排浸一晚溫泉，當然亦可選擇箱根浸，但平均會比較貴(除左窮人恩物一の湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n如果東京要住airbnb，通常都無得寄存行李，要去車站租Locker，個人唔太prefer(除非你樓下就係主要車站)<br />\n<br />\n浸溫泉其實就豐儉由人，例如芦ノ湖一の湯我上Jalan望下而家book都係每位7000yen，不連稅但包兩餐，其實唔貴得過番東京住。其實我覺得反而住東京先貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n輕井澤果個好有用 thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea58eb71f8542f63a13e7a3efc8449a81896a76","tid":370910,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:50:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去咁多地方 邊玩同睇得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係架 但因為budget有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n決定咗每日來回既話<br />\n咁只可以揀果日行程睇少啲野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有下次手頭鬆啲果陣再去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明知自已 budget 有限就好心咪貪心學人去咁多近郊地方啦，冇錢咁樣玩搵自已笨。</blockquote><br />\n河口湖點都要住返晚溫泉酒店，好正<br />\n<br />\n川越同江之島都可以即日來回<br />\n箱根加河口湖預三日左右</blockquote><br />\n依家cut 左河口湖同川越喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab40820a37cfcf65df8de3c580e795251aa6653","tid":370910,"uid":92462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T14:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去咁多地方 邊玩同睇得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係架 但因為budget有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n決定咗每日來回既話<br />\n咁只可以揀果日行程睇少啲野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有下次手頭鬆啲果陣再去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明知自已 budget 有限就好心咪貪心學人去咁多近郊地方啦，冇錢咁樣玩搵自已笨。</blockquote><br />\n河口湖點都要住返晚溫泉酒店，好正<br />\n<br />\n川越同江之島都可以即日來回<br />\n箱根加河口湖預三日左右</blockquote><br />\n依家cut 左河口湖同川越喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n川越聽人講好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm